{"tid":1546973,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【明信片行動】想策動全球國家幫香港？機會來喇，向全球派呢堆明信片求救啦！","createTime":"2019-09-06T13:35:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T14:33:01.000Z","uid":54684,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"ff3f559a37f27a6dad2758ce23848c4edfd48f00","tid":1546973,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T13:35:25.000Z","msg":"好多外國人好想幫香港，但完全唔知點幫，於是我之前出左post︰<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><strong>外國人心聲︰得喇我知香港喇，咁我可以點幫手呀大佬？你講至得架！點幫呀？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1472787\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1472787</a></strong></blockquote><br />\n<blockquote><strong>外國網民︰我想幫香港呀！但完全唔識做！得個加國港人叫我&quot;spread the news&quot;.....<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529160\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529160</a></strong></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;大家都可以入post睇睇。<br />\n建議好多，有sanctions，人權法，BNO，醫療物資，入境黑名單.....等等<br />\n<br />\n依家，正值美國，英國出招幫香港前夕，<br />\n政府出招想confuse外國，搏佢減辣，搏佢暫緩<br />\n有見及此，有朋友整左堆<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">明信片</span></strong>，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">將呢3個月既動人時刻放入去，宣傳香港既痛苦<br />\n背面就附上點樣將同情化為行動，去take actions support香港</span></strong><br />\n務求策動全球國家幫香港<br />\n<br />\n暫時以英國，美國為主攻，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">佢畀左D samples出來<br />\n睇下大家咩反應，反應好既話，confirm完資料再remove &quot;SAMPLE&quot;水印</span></strong><br />\n國際versions可以再推出咁話<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Side A︰</strong>明信片正面    暫時呢幾款<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x6xnD4X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx6xnD4X.png&h=1422b704&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6ezM5Xg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6ezM5Xg.png&h=2634e444&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZtAc1ii.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZtAc1ii.png&h=7df7d51d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rCMLBRE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrCMLBRE.png&h=f66d7999&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Un9AY41.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUn9AY41.png&h=9e636add&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Side B︰</strong>明信片背面  教人點幫香港   暫時呢幾款 (視乎對象地區)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7FmoowH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7FmoowH.png&h=c0d73b65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vb1GUDo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVb1GUDo.png&h=3c3288ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我代佢PO  大家點睇"},{"pid":"15e42ed3ff970a4031aebfba5322f0a9c5618e2d","tid":1546973,"uid":54684,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T13:35:29.000Z","msg":"佢話︰<br />\n1) <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">留學生/外國巴絲</span></strong>就最啱派，直接係當地改變當地人既心態，去當地地鐵站派去鬧市派，<strong>宣傳直達外國民眾，影響英美國會議員取態</strong>，呢個係個主要usage<br />\n2) 本地派畀旅客又得，再唔係Twitter send圖畀外國政客又得<br />\n3) For 國家/國際版既指引，視乎反應可以後加<br />\n4) 完全和平，完全和理非，安全，但又可以影響外國行動<br />\n5) 附上QR codes，畀外國人睇深入D，連去反送中網站，及中英聯合聲明被撕毀既情況 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">(但sample度highlight紅色，因為未confirm應該用邊條link，唔知邊度有警暴list / 中英聯合聲明被撕毀既資料 等等，要英文and整理好)</span></strong><br />\n6) 重有Twitter hashtags畀人follow tweets"},{"pid":"4cf7b4697d659e6626cbc244f336277f2c807a7a","tid":1546973,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T13:35:53.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"84bd30cf63b76b64419bcc061047181605f95992","tid":1546973,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T13:36:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4208336a1a594b3fe1736f31f48f77337d094b8a","tid":1546973,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T13:37:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fc405f9369ef8c0552f6cd838f7c5d3e2a9b62b","tid":1546973,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T13:38:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"583118f526fa50a19f4a5cdfc6e432f23620ad23","tid":1546973,"uid":261544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T13:39:29.000Z","msg":"gd, p牌仔無得推，但push"},{"pid":"a3781195c762b8becd39adfdb81ad161d61b7d91","tid":1546973,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T13:39:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32b59f89eb2e3e3994058c40aac2ef8fe14e8e74","tid":1546973,"uid":261544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T13:40:28.000Z","msg":"如果有，我會派"},{"pid":"3cbabd32034643c94b730d457debc7742c6f2954","tid":1546973,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T13:41:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e0150fc1744625413d057f2878b0b550b85cd93","tid":1546973,"uid":296614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T13:43:12.000Z","msg":"推唔到<br />\n不過呢個idea幾好<br />\n利申倫敦絲可以幫手派"},{"pid":"efffe2bdd6670aada5ef601197d93eb342b0cac5","tid